        <imsmd:language>en</imsmd:language>
        <imsmd:description>
          <imsmd:langstring xml:lang="en">Use a unit circle tool to explore cosine values in different quadrants. Determine the cos &#xd8; values for angles between 0&#xb0; and 360&#xb0;. Observe the symmetry and patterns of the functions to predict the behaviour of cos &#xd8; in different quadrants. Observe the graph animate and visually connect it with the unit circle tool and table values. Extend cos &#xd8; for angles beyond 360&#xb0;. Find out how trigonometry relates to the real world. This learning object is one in a series of nine objects. Three objects in the series are also packaged as a combined learning object.</imsmd:langstring>
        </imsmd:description>
